Paul Smith (Australian actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Paul_Smith_(Australian_actor) 0 Paul Smith (born 1968 in Sydney) is a former Australian actor, who started his career as a child performer, he is most known for his role as the original Simon Kelly in the television sitcom Hey Dad...!, and as Steve in the children's television series The Henderson Kids.
